                <h1>Essential Types of Background Checks for Hiring</h1>
                <p>Background checks come in various forms to ensure the safety and security of hiring processes. Common types include criminal record checks, employment history verification, credit checks, and education verification. Each serves a unique purpose and helps employers make informed decisions about potential candidates.</p>
